  EffectDiscription_ENG: "[Digivolve][Cupimon]: Cost 5 \n\nWhen you would play this
    card, if you don't have a level 5 or lower Digimon, reduce the play cost by 5.\n[On
    Play] [Start of Your Main Phase] Reveal the top 3 cards of your deck. Add 1 card
    with the [Angel]/[Archangel]/[Three Great Angels]/[Seven Great Demon Lords]\_trait
    among them to your hand. Trash the rest.\n[End of Your Turn] [Once Per Turn]
    By placing one of your level 6 Digimon on top of your security stack, this Digimon
    may digivolve into [Lucemon: Chaos Mode] in the trash without paying the cost."
